<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>ArchiveBox Plugin Marketplace | abx-plugins</title>
    <meta
      name="description"
      content="Browse the ArchiveBox plugin ecosystem, including abx-plugins hooks, config options, source links, and example commands for ArchiveBox, abx-dl, and related web archiving tools."
    >
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=IBM+Plex+Mono:wght@400;500&family=Space+Grotesk:wght@400;500;700&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    >
    <style>
      :root {
        --bg: #0f1114;
        --bg-accent: #1a1d22;
        --surface: rgba(26, 29, 34, 0.92);
        --surface-strong: #1e2126;
        --ink: #f0f0f3;
        --muted: #a1a1aa;
        --line: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        --accent: #2dd4bf;
        --accent-soft: rgba(45, 212, 191, 0.12);
        --warm: #f59e0b;
        --shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
        --radius: 0px;
        --hero-badge-height: 64px;
      }

      * {
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      html {
        scroll-behavior: smooth;
      }

      body {
        margin: 0;
        min-height: 100vh;
        color: var(--ink);
        background:
          radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(45, 212, 191, 0.06), transparent 30%),
          radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.04), transparent 28%),
          var(--bg);
        font-family: "Space Grotesk", sans-serif;
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }

      a {
        color: inherit;
      }

      code,
      pre,
      input {
        font-family: "IBM Plex Mono", monospace;
      }

      .page-shell {
        width: calc(100vw - 24px);
        margin: 0 12px;
        padding: 20px 0 48px;
      }

      .hero {
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
        padding: 36px;
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
        border-radius: 0;
        background:
          linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(26, 29, 34, 0.95), rgba(20, 22, 26, 0.92)),
          linear-gradient(120deg, rgba(45, 212, 191, 0.06), transparent 60%);
        box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      }

      .hero::after {
        content: "";
        position: absolute;
        inset: auto -80px -100px auto;
        width: 260px;
        height: 260px;
        border-radius: 50%;
        background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.15), transparent 70%);
        pointer-events: none;
      }

      .hero-top {
        display: flex;
        gap: 18px;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: flex-start;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
      }

      .hero-actions {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: flex-end;
        flex: 1 1 220px;
      }

      .eyebrow {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 10px;
        margin-bottom: 12px;
        font-size: 0.84rem;
        letter-spacing: 0.14em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: var(--warm);
      }

      .eyebrow::before {
        content: "";
        width: 40px;
        height: 1px;
        background: currentColor;
      }

      h1 {
        margin: 0;
        max-width: 52ch;
        font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 8vw, 4.2rem);
        line-height: 0.94;
        letter-spacing: -0.05em;
      }

      .hero-copy {
        max-width: 70ch;
        margin: 18px 0 0;
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: 1rem;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }

      .hero-meta {
        display: flex;
        gap: 12px;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
      }

      .stat {
        min-width: 140px;
        min-height: var(--hero-badge-height);
        padding: 14px 16px;
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
        border-radius: 0;
        background: var(--bg-accent);
      }

      .stat strong {
        display: block;
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        line-height: 1.1;
      }

      .stat span {
        font-size: 0.82rem;
        color: var(--muted);
      }

      .stat-link {
        display: block;
        min-width: 140px;
        text-decoration: none;
        color: inherit;
      }

      .stat-link:hover {
        transform: translateY(-1px);
      }

      .stat-link--cta {
        background: var(--surface-strong);
        border: 2px solid rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.55);
        box-shadow: 0 10px 28px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        animation: cta-border-color-cycle 2.4s linear infinite;
      }

      .stat-link--cta strong,
      .stat-link--cta span {
        position: relative;
        z-index: 1;
      }

      .stat-link--cta strong {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 8px;
      }

      .cta-plus {
        display: inline-grid;
        place-items: center;
        width: 20px;
        height: 20px;
        border-radius: 0;
        background: rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.15);
        color: var(--warm);
        font-family: "IBM Plex Mono", monospace;
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        line-height: 1;
      }

      @keyframes cta-border-color-cycle {
        0% {
          border-color: rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.65);
        }
        33% {
          border-color: rgba(45, 212, 191, 0.65);
        }
        66% {
          border-color: rgba(229, 184, 76, 0.72);
        }
        100% {
          border-color: rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.65);
        }
      }

      .toolbar {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr) auto;
        gap: 14px;
        margin-top: 28px;
      }

      .hero-example {
        position: relative;
        z-index: 1;
        margin-top: 24px;
        padding: 20px;
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
        border-radius: 0;
        background: var(--bg-accent);
        backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
      }

      .hero-example-header {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: flex-start;
        gap: 16px;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
      }

      .hero-example-title {
        margin: 0;
        font-size: 0.82rem;
        letter-spacing: 0.14em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: var(--warm);
      }

      .hero-example-copy {
        margin: 8px 0 0;
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        line-height: 1.55;
      }

      .hero-runner-links {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 8px;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
      }

      .hero-runner-links span {
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: 0.84rem;
      }

      .runner-link {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        padding: 8px 12px;
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
        border-radius: 0;
        background: var(--bg-accent);
        color: var(--accent);
        text-decoration: none;
        font-size: 0.84rem;
      }

      .runner-link:hover {
        transform: translateY(-1px);
      }

      .hero-code-block {
        margin-top: 16px;
        overflow: hidden;
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
        border-radius: 0;
        background: linear-gradient(180deg, #1a1f25, #131619);
        color: #e4e4e7;
      }

      .hero-code-toolbar {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 12px;
        padding: 14px 16px;
        border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
        background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02));
      }

      .hero-code-meta {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 10px;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
      }

      .hero-code-kicker {
        color: rgba(240, 240, 243, 0.72);
        font-size: 0.78rem;
        letter-spacing: 0.08em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
      }

      .hero-code-meta code {
        padding: 4px 10px;
        border-radius: 0;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
        color: #e4e4e7;
        font-size: 0.84rem;
      }

      .copy-button {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        min-width: 82px;
        padding: 9px 13px;
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.14);
        border-radius: 0;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
        color: #e4e4e7;
        font: inherit;
        font-size: 0.84rem;
        cursor: pointer;
      }

      .copy-button:hover {
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.16);
      }

      .hero-code-block pre {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 16px;
        overflow-x: auto;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        line-height: 1.7;
      }

      .hero-code-block code {
        display: block;
        min-width: min-content;
      }

      .code-comment {
        color: rgba(247, 241, 230, 0.48);
      }

      .code-command {
        color: #7dd3fc;
      }

      .code-option {
        color: #fbbf24;
      }

      .code-string {
        color: #bef264;
      }

      .code-env {
        color: #fda4af;
      }

      .code-boolean {
        color: #fdba74;
      }

      .code-value {
        color: #cbd5e1;
      }

      .install-details {
        margin-top: 14px;
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
        border-radius: 0;
        background: linear-gradient(180deg, #1a1f25, #131619);
        color: #e4e4e7;
      }

      .install-details summary {
        cursor: pointer;
        list-style: none;
        padding: 14px 16px;
        font-size: 0.92rem;
        font-weight: 500;
      }

      .install-details summary::-webkit-details-marker {
        display: none;
      }

      .install-details summary::after {
        content: "+";
        float: right;
        color: var(--accent);
        font-family: "IBM Plex Mono", monospace;
      }

      .install-details[open] summary::after {
        content: "-";
      }

      .install-details pre {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0 16px 16px;
        white-space: pre-wrap;
        word-break: break-word;
        font-size: 0.86rem;
        line-height: 1.65;
      }

      .searchbox {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 12px;
        padding: 0 18px;
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
        border-radius: 0;
        background: var(--bg-accent);
      }

      .searchbox input {
        width: 100%;
        border: 0;
        outline: 0;
        background: transparent;
        padding: 17px 0;
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        color: var(--ink);
      }

      .searchbox svg {
        color: var(--accent);
        flex: 0 0 auto;
      }

      .result-count {
        align-self: center;
        padding: 12px 16px;
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
        border-radius: 0;
        background: var(--bg-accent);
        color: var(--muted);
        white-space: nowrap;
      }

      .gallery {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(min(100%, 520px), 1fr));
        gap: 18px;
        margin-top: 24px;
        align-items: start;
      }

      .plugin-card {
        --card-tint: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
        --card-border: var(--line);
        --card-accent: var(--accent);
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
        border-radius: 0;
        background: var(--bg-accent);
        box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        transition: transform 180ms ease, border-color 180ms ease, box-shadow 180ms ease, background 180ms ease;
      }

      .plugin-card--snapshot {
        --card-tint: rgba(73, 154, 84, 0.08);
        --card-border: rgba(73, 154, 84, 0.3);
        --card-accent: #4ade80;
      }

      .plugin-card--crawl-only {
        --card-tint: rgba(96, 165, 250, 0.08);
        --card-border: rgba(96, 165, 250, 0.3);
        --card-accent: #60a5fa;
      }

      .plugin-card--binary-only {
        --card-tint: rgba(161, 161, 170, 0.08);
        --card-border: rgba(161, 161, 170, 0.3);
        --card-accent: #a1a1aa;
      }

      .plugin-card[hidden] {
        display: none;
      }

      .plugin-card:hover {
        transform: translateY(-2px);
        border-color: var(--card-border);
      }

      .plugin-card[open] > .plugin-body {
        display: none;
      }

      .plugin-card.modal-active {
        border-color: var(--card-accent);
        box-shadow: 0 0 0 2px var(--card-accent), 0 14px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        transform: translateY(-2px);
      }

      .plugin-modal {
        width: min(900px, calc(100vw - 40px));
        max-height: calc(100vh - 80px);
        overflow-y: auto;
        margin: auto;
        padding: 0;
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
        border-radius: 0;
        background: var(--surface-strong);
        color: var(--ink);
        box-shadow: 0 32px 80px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
        animation: modalIn 200ms ease;
      }

      .plugin-modal::backdrop {
        background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
        backdrop-filter: blur(4px);
      }

      @keyframes modalIn {
        from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(16px) scale(0.97); }
        to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0) scale(1); }
      }

      .plugin-modal-header {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: space-between;
        padding: 20px 22px 0;
        gap: 14px;
      }

      .plugin-modal-header-left {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 12px;
        min-width: 0;
      }

      .plugin-modal-header h2 {
        margin: 0;
        font-size: 1.4rem;
      }

      .plugin-modal-close {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        width: 36px;
        height: 36px;
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
        border-radius: 0;
        background: var(--surface);
        cursor: pointer;
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        color: var(--muted);
        transition: background 120ms ease, color 120ms ease;
        flex-shrink: 0;
      }

      .plugin-modal-close:hover {
        background: var(--bg-accent);
        color: var(--ink);
      }

      .plugin-modal > .plugin-body {
        padding: 0 22px 22px;
      }

      .plugin-modal-description {
        color: var(--muted);
        margin: 0 0 12px;
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        line-height: 1.5;
      }

      .plugin-card summary {
        position: relative;
        display: block;
        list-style: none;
        padding: 22px 68px 20px 22px;
        cursor: pointer;
        container-type: inline-size;
      }

      .plugin-card summary::-webkit-details-marker {
        display: none;
      }

      .plugin-icon {
        display: inline-grid;
        place-items: center;
        width: 36px;
        height: 36px;
        border-radius: 0;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
        color: var(--card-accent);
      }

      .plugin-icon .abx-output-icon {
        display: inline-grid;
        place-items: center;
      }

      .plugin-icon .abx-output-icon svg {
        width: 18px;
        height: 18px;
      }

      .plugin-main {
        min-width: 0;
        display: grid;
        gap: 10px;
      }

      .plugin-title-row {
        display: block;
      }

      .plugin-main h2 {
        margin: 0;
        font-size: clamp(1.25rem, 6.2cqi, 3rem);
        line-height: 0.96;
        letter-spacing: -0.04em;
        text-wrap: balance;
        overflow-wrap: anywhere;
      }



      .plugin-slug {
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: 0.86rem;
        letter-spacing: 0.02em;
      }

      .plugin-summary-description {
        margin: 0;
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        line-height: 1.55;
      }

      .plugin-header-meta {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 10px;
        flex: 0 0 auto;
        white-space: nowrap;
      }

      .plugin-order {
        font-family: "IBM Plex Mono", monospace;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        font-weight: 500;
        letter-spacing: 0.02em;
        color: var(--card-accent);
      }

      .plugin-language {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        width: 20px;
        height: 20px;
        color: var(--ink);
        flex: 0 0 auto;
      }

      .plugin-language--python {
        color: #346f9c;
      }

      .plugin-language--javascript {
        color: #7a6200;
      }

      .plugin-subline {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 8px;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
      }

      .plugin-summary-facts {
        display: grid;
        gap: 6px;
        margin-top: 2px;
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: 0.87rem;
      }

      .plugin-summary-facts strong {
        color: var(--ink);
        font-weight: 500;
      }

      .chip {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 6px;
        padding: 6px 10px;
        border-radius: 0;
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
        background: var(--bg-accent);
        font-size: 0.84rem;
        color: var(--muted);
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.06em;
      }

      .chip--link {
        text-decoration: none;
        color: var(--accent);
        cursor: pointer;
      }

      .chip--link:hover {
        background: var(--accent-soft);
        border-color: var(--accent);
      }

      .chip--binary-summary {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: baseline;
        gap: 4px;
        padding: 2px 8px;
        border-radius: 0;
        font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
        font-size: 0.82rem;
        text-transform: none;
        letter-spacing: normal;
      }

      .chip--binary-summary small {
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: 0.8rem;
      }

      .chip--binary {
        display: inline-grid;
        gap: 4px;
        align-items: start;
        padding: 10px 12px;
        border-radius: 0;
        text-transform: none;
        letter-spacing: normal;
      }

      .chip--binary strong,
      .chip--binary code {
        color: var(--ink);
      }

      .chip--binary small {
        display: block;
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: 0.8rem;
        line-height: 1.45;
        word-break: break-word;
      }

      .chip--mime {
        text-transform: none;
        letter-spacing: normal;
        font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
        font-size: 0.82rem;
        gap: 4px;
      }

      .chip--mime-html     { background: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.10); border-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.25); color: #2563eb; }
      .chip--mime-text     { background: rgba(107, 114, 128, 0.10); border-color: rgba(107, 114, 128, 0.25); color: #4b5563; }
      .chip--mime-image    { background: rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.10); border-color: rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.25); color: #7c3aed; }
      .chip--mime-media    { background: rgba(236, 72, 153, 0.10); border-color: rgba(236, 72, 153, 0.25); color: #db2777; }
      .chip--mime-data     { background: rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.10); border-color: rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.25); color: #b45309; }
      .chip--mime-code     { background: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.10); border-color: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.25); color: #059669; }
      .chip--mime-doc      { background: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.10); border-color: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.25); color: #dc2626; }
      .chip--mime-archive  { background: rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.10); border-color: rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.25); color: #4f46e5; }
      .chip--mime-binary   { background: rgba(75, 85, 99, 0.10); border-color: rgba(75, 85, 99, 0.25); color: #374151; }

      .plugin-corner-icon {
        position: absolute;
        top: 18px;
        right: 18px;
        display: grid;
        place-items: center;
        width: 36px;
        height: 36px;
        pointer-events: none;
      }

      .plugin-body {
        padding: 0 22px 22px;
      }

      .actions {
        display: flex;
        gap: 10px;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        margin-bottom: 18px;
      }

      .button-link {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 10px;
        padding: 10px 14px;
        border-radius: 0;
        border: 1px solid rgba(45, 212, 191, 0.2);
        background: var(--accent-soft);
        color: var(--accent);
        text-decoration: none;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
      }

      .button-link--hero {
        border-color: var(--line);
        background: var(--bg-accent);
        box-shadow: none;
      }

      .section-title {
        margin: 20px 0 10px;
        font-size: 0.82rem;
        letter-spacing: 0.14em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: var(--warm);
      }

      .command-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr));
        gap: 12px;
      }

      .run-tabs {
        overflow: hidden;
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
        border-radius: 0;
        background: linear-gradient(180deg, #1a1f25, #131619);
        color: #e4e4e7;
      }

      .run-tabs-bar {
        display: flex;
        border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
      }

      .run-tab {
        flex: 1;
        padding: 9px 14px;
        border: none;
        border-bottom: 2px solid transparent;
        background: transparent;
        color: rgba(228, 228, 231, 0.45);
        font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
        font-size: 0.78rem;
        font-weight: 500;
        cursor: pointer;
        text-align: center;
        transition: color 120ms ease, border-color 120ms ease;
      }

      .run-tab code {
        font-size: inherit;
        color: inherit;
      }

      .run-tab:hover {
        color: rgba(228, 228, 231, 0.72);
      }

      .run-tab.active {
        color: #e4e4e7;
        border-bottom-color: var(--accent);
      }

      .run-tab-panel {
        display: none;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 14px 16px;
        overflow-x: auto;
        font-size: 0.88rem;
        line-height: 1.7;
      }

      .run-tab-panel.active {
        display: block;
      }

      .run-tab-panel code {
        display: block;
        min-width: min-content;
      }

      .empty-state {
        padding: 16px;
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
        border-radius: 0;
        background: var(--bg-accent);
      }

      .hook-card {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 10px;
        padding: 10px 14px;
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
        border-radius: 0;
        background: var(--bg-accent);
      }

      .hook-card-file {
        font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
        font-size: 0.88rem;
      }

      .hook-card-file a {
        color: var(--ink);
        text-decoration: none;
      }

      .hook-card-file a:hover {
        color: var(--accent);
      }

      .hook-card-chips {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 6px;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
      }

      .hook-card-phase {
        margin-left: auto;
        font-size: 0.84rem;
        color: var(--muted);
        white-space: nowrap;
      }

      .chip--lang {
        padding: 4px 6px;
        line-height: 1;
      }

      .chip--lang-py {
        border-color: rgba(250, 204, 21, 0.35);
        background: rgba(250, 204, 21, 0.1);
        color: #facc15;
      }

      .chip--lang-js {
        border-color: rgba(96, 165, 250, 0.35);
        background: rgba(96, 165, 250, 0.1);
        color: #60a5fa;
      }

      .chip--fg {
        border-color: rgba(74, 222, 128, 0.35);
        background: rgba(74, 222, 128, 0.1);
        color: #4ade80;
      }

      .chip--bg-finite {
        border-color: rgba(34, 139, 34, 0.4);
        background: rgba(34, 139, 34, 0.12);
        color: #22c55e;
      }

      .chip--bg-daemon {
        border-color: rgba(251, 146, 60, 0.4);
        background: rgba(251, 146, 60, 0.12);
        color: #fb923c;
      }

      .command-card pre,
      .config-card pre {
        margin: 0;
        white-space: pre-wrap;
        word-break: break-word;
        font-size: 0.86rem;
        line-height: 1.55;
      }

      .note {
        margin: 10px 0 0;
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        line-height: 1.55;
      }

      .hook-list {
        display: grid;
        gap: 6px;
      }

      .config-table-wrap {
        overflow-x: auto;
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
        border-radius: 0;
        background: var(--bg-accent);
      }

      .config-table {
        width: 100%;
        border-collapse: collapse;
        font-size: 0.86rem;
        table-layout: fixed;
      }

      .config-table colgroup .col-key { width: 38%; }
      .config-table colgroup .col-default { width: 24%; }
      .config-table colgroup .col-type { width: 18%; }
      .config-table colgroup .col-aliases { width: 20%; }

      .config-table th {
        text-align: left;
        padding: 10px 12px;
        font-size: 0.82rem;
        font-weight: 500;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.06em;
        color: var(--muted);
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
        white-space: nowrap;
      }

      .config-table td {
        padding: 8px 12px;
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
        vertical-align: top;
      }

      .config-table td:nth-child(1) code { white-space: nowrap; }
      .config-table td:nth-child(2) { word-break: break-word; }
      .config-table td:nth-child(3) { white-space: nowrap; }
      .config-table td:nth-child(4) { word-break: break-word; }

      .config-table tbody tr:last-child td {
        border-bottom: none;
      }

      .config-table tbody tr:hover {
        background: rgba(45, 212, 191, 0.04);
      }

      .config-table code {
        font-size: 0.82rem;
      }

      .config-table td:nth-child(1) code {
        color: #7dd3fc;
      }

      .config-table td:nth-child(2) {
        word-break: break-word;
      }

      .config-table td:nth-child(3) code {
        color: #fbbf24;
      }

      .config-table small {
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: 0.84rem;
      }

      .config-key-desc {
        display: block;
        margin-top: 2px;
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: 0.84rem;
        font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
      }

      .config-table-muted {
        color: var(--muted);
      }

      .cfg-default {
        font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
        font-size: 0.84rem;
      }

      .cfg-bool-true { color: #4ade80; }
      .cfg-bool-false { color: #f87171; }
      .cfg-number { color: #7dd3fc; }
      .cfg-string { color: #bef264; }
      .cfg-null { color: var(--muted); font-style: italic; }
      .cfg-bracket { color: var(--muted); }
      .cfg-obj-key { color: #7dd3fc; }

      .cfg-array {
        padding-left: 14px;
      }

      .cfg-array-item::after {
        content: ",";
        color: var(--muted);
      }

      .cfg-array-item:last-child::after {
        content: "";
      }

      .cfg-obj {
        padding-left: 14px;
      }

      .plugin-info-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr));
        gap: 12px;
      }

      .plugin-info-card {
        padding: 16px;
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
        border-radius: 0;
        background: var(--bg-accent);
      }

      .plugin-info-card span {
        display: block;
        margin-bottom: 8px;
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: 0.78rem;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      }

      .plugin-info-card p {
        margin: 0;
        color: var(--muted);
        line-height: 1.55;
      }

      .pill-list {
        display: flex;
        gap: 8px;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
      }

      .config-card strong {
        display: block;
        margin-bottom: 6px;
        font-size: 1rem;
        word-break: break-word;
      }

      .config-card p {
        margin: 0 0 10px;
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: 0.93rem;
        line-height: 1.55;
      }

      .config-meta {
        display: grid;
        gap: 6px;
        margin-bottom: 12px;
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: 0.84rem;
      }

      .config-meta code {
        font-size: 0.84rem;
      }

      .page-footer {
        margin-top: 26px;
        padding: 28px;
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
        border-radius: 0;
        background: var(--bg-accent);
        box-shadow: 0 16px 42px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        color: var(--muted);
      }

      .page-footer a {
        color: var(--accent);
      }

      .footer-intro {
        display: grid;
        gap: 12px;
        margin-bottom: 24px;
        max-width: 980px;
        margin-left: auto;
        margin-right: auto;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .footer-intro h2 {
        margin: 0;
        color: var(--ink);
        font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 2.4vw, 2rem);
        line-height: 1;
        letter-spacing: -0.04em;
      }

      .footer-intro p {
        margin: 0;
        max-width: 92ch;
        margin-left: auto;
        margin-right: auto;
        font-size: 0.98rem;
        line-height: 1.7;
      }

      .footer-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr));
        gap: 18px;
      }

      .footer-card {
        min-height: 100%;
        padding: 20px 20px 18px;
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
        border-radius: 0;
        background: var(--bg-accent);
      }

      .footer-card h3 {
        margin: 0 0 10px;
        color: var(--ink);
        font-size: 1rem;
      }

      .footer-card p {
        margin: 0 0 12px;
        font-size: 0.92rem;
        line-height: 1.65;
      }

      .footer-link-list {
        display: grid;
        gap: 10px;
      }

      .footer-link-item {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 34px 1fr;
        gap: 10px;
        align-items: start;
        padding: 10px 12px;
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
        border-radius: 0;
        background: var(--bg-accent);
        text-decoration: none;
      }

      .footer-link-item:hover {
        border-color: rgba(45, 212, 191, 0.3);
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
      }

      .footer-link-icon {
        display: inline-grid;
        place-items: center;
        width: 34px;
        height: 34px;
        border-radius: 0;
        background: var(--accent-soft);
        color: var(--accent);
        font-size: 1rem;
        line-height: 1;
      }

      .footer-link-copy {
        display: grid;
        gap: 2px;
      }

      .footer-link-copy strong {
        color: var(--ink);
        font-size: 0.94rem;
        line-height: 1.2;
      }

      .footer-link-copy span {
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: 0.84rem;
        line-height: 1.45;
      }

      .footer-link-copy code {
        font-size: 0.84rem;
      }

      .footer-link-inline {
        text-decoration: none;
      }

      .footer-card-subtitle {
        margin: 0 0 14px;
        color: var(--warm);
        font-size: 0.8rem;
        letter-spacing: 0.08em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
      }

      .footer-meta {
        display: flex;
        gap: 12px;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: center;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        margin-top: 18px;
        padding-top: 18px;
        border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
        font-size: 0.88rem;
      }

      .empty-state {
        margin-top: 24px;
        text-align: center;
        color: var(--muted);
      }

      @media (max-width: 720px) {
        .page-shell {
          width: calc(100vw - 12px);
          margin: 0 6px;
          padding-top: 12px;
        }

        .hero {
          padding: 24px;
        }

        .hero-example-header,
        .hero-code-toolbar {
          flex-direction: column;
          align-items: flex-start;
        }

        .copy-button {
          width: 100%;
        }

        .toolbar,
        .plugin-card summary {
          grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }

        .plugin-card summary {
          align-items: flex-start;
        }

        .plugin-corner-icon {
          display: none;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="page-shell">
      <section class="hero">
        <div class="hero-top">
          <div>
            <div class="eyebrow">Save the content that matters most.</div>
            <h1>ArchiveBox Plugin Gallery</h1>
            <p class="hero-copy">
              Browse the plugins that ArchiveBox &amp; abx-dl use to archive content from websites.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="hero-actions">
            <a
              class="stat stat-link stat-link--cta button-link--hero"
              href="https://github.com/ArchiveBox/abx-plugins/pulls"
              target="_blank"
            >
              <strong><span class="cta-plus">+</span> Submit</strong>
              <center><span>a new plugin</span></center>
            </a>
          </div>
          <div class="hero-meta">
            <div class="stat">
              <strong>{{ site.plugin_count }}</strong>
              <span>Plugins</span>
            </div>
            <!--<div class="stat">
              <strong>{{ site.hook_count }}</strong>
              <span>Hook scripts</span>
            </div>-->
            <!--<div class="stat">
              <strong>{{ site.config_count }}</strong>
              <span>Config Options</span>
            </div>-->
          </div>
        </div>

        <section class="hero-example" aria-labelledby="quickstart-heading">
          <div class="hero-example-header">
            <div>
              <h2 class="hero-example-title" id="quickstart-heading">Run The Selected Plugin</h2>
              <p class="hero-example-copy">
                Pick some plugins below and copy the command to run them.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="hero-runner-links">
              <span>Get:</span>
              <a class="runner-link" href="https://github.com/ArchiveBox/abx-dl#readme" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">abx-dl</a>
              <a class="runner-link" href="https://github.com/ArchiveBox/ArchiveBox#readme" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">ArchiveBox</a>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="hero-code-block">
            <div class="hero-code-toolbar">
              <div class="hero-code-meta">
                <span class="hero-code-kicker">Quick Start</span>
                <code id="selected-plugin-name">abx-dl</code>
              </div>
              <button type="button" class="copy-button" id="copy-example-button">Copy</button>
            </div>
            <pre><code id="hero-command-example" aria-live="polite"></code></pre>
          </div>

          <details class="install-details">
            <summary>Expand to see pip install details</summary>
            <pre><code data-highlight-shell>pip install abx-dl
abx-dl install
mkdir archive
cd archive
abx-dl 'https://example.com'</code></pre>
          </details>
        </section>
      </section>

      <div class="toolbar">
        <label class="searchbox" for="plugin-search">
          <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8">
            <circle cx="11" cy="11" r="7"></circle>
            <path d="M20 20l-3.5-3.5"></path>
          </svg>
          <input
            id="plugin-search"
            type="search"
            placeholder="Filter by plugin name, hook, config key, or description"
            autocomplete="off"
            spellcheck="false"
          >
        </label>
        <div class="result-count"><span id="visible-count">{{ site.plugin_count }}</span> / {{ site.plugin_count }} visible</div>
      </div>

      <main class="gallery" id="plugin-gallery">
        {% for plugin in site.plugins %}
        <details
          id="{{ plugin.name }}"
          class="plugin-card{% if 'Snapshot' in plugin.phases %} plugin-card--snapshot{% elif plugin.phases == ['Crawl'] %} plugin-card--crawl-only{% elif plugin.phases == ['Binary'] %} plugin-card--binary-only{% endif %}"
          data-search="{{ plugin.search_text }}"
          data-hero-plugin="{{ plugin.name }}"
          data-hero-abx-command="{% if 'Snapshot' in plugin.phases %}uvx abx-dl --plugins {{ plugin.name }} 'https://example.com'{% else %}uvx {{ plugin.commands.abx_dl }}{% endif %}"
          data-hero-archivebox-command="{{ plugin.commands.archivebox }}"
        >
          <summary>
            <div class="plugin-main">
              <div class="plugin-title-row">
                <h2>{{ plugin.display_title }}</h2>
              </div>
              <div class="plugin-slug"><code>{{ plugin.name }}</code></div>
              {% if plugin.description %}
              <p class="plugin-summary-description">{{ plugin.description }}</p>
              {% endif %}
              <div class="plugin-subline">
                {% if plugin.display_order is not none %}
                <span class="plugin-order">#{{ "%02d"|format(plugin.display_order) }}</span>
                {% endif %}
                {% if plugin.primary_language == "python" %}
                <span class="plugin-language plugin-language--python" title="Predominantly Python hooks" aria-label="Predominantly Python hooks">
                  <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" fill="none">
                    <path d="M12 3c-4.4 0-4.1 1.9-4.1 1.9v2h4.2v.6H6.2S3 7.1 3 12c0 4.9 2.8 4.7 2.8 4.7h1.7v-2.4s-.1-2.8 2.7-2.8h4.6s2.6 0 2.6-2.6V4.6S17.8 3 12 3Z" fill="currentColor" opacity="0.92"></path>
                    <path d="M12 21c4.4 0 4.1-1.9 4.1-1.9v-2h-4.2v-.6h5.9S21 16.9 21 12c0-4.9-2.8-4.7-2.8-4.7h-1.7v2.4s.1 2.8-2.7 2.8h-4.6S6.6 12.5 6.6 15v4.4S6.2 21 12 21Z" fill="currentColor" opacity="0.6"></path>
                    <circle cx="9.3" cy="5.6" r="1" fill="#fff"></circle>
                    <circle cx="14.7" cy="18.4" r="1" fill="#fff"></circle>
                  </svg>
                </span>
                {% elif plugin.primary_language == "javascript" %}
                <span class="plugin-language plugin-language--javascript" title="Predominantly JavaScript hooks" aria-label="Predominantly JavaScript hooks">
                  <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false">
                    <rect x="4.5" y="4.5" width="15" height="15" rx="2.5" fill="currentColor" opacity="0.2"></rect>
                    <path d="M10.3 8.1v6.4c0 2-1 3.4-3.1 3.4-1.7 0-2.7-.9-3.2-2l1.7-1c.3.6.6 1.1 1.4 1.1.7 0 1.1-.3 1.1-1.5V8.1h2.1Zm7.1 1.7c-.4-.7-1-.9-1.7-.9-.7 0-1.4.3-1.4 1 0 .7.5 1 1.8 1.4 1.8.6 3 1.3 3 3.3 0 2.1-1.7 3.3-3.9 3.3-2 0-3.2-.8-4-2.1l1.7-1.2c.5.8 1.1 1.4 2.2 1.4.9 0 1.6-.4 1.6-1.1 0-.8-.6-1-2-1.5-1.7-.6-2.8-1.3-2.8-3.2 0-1.9 1.6-3.1 3.7-3.1 1.4 0 2.5.4 3.3 1.6l-1.5 1.1Z" fill="currentColor"></path>
                  </svg>
                </span>
                {% endif %}
                
                {% for phase in plugin.phases %}
                <span class="chip">{{ phase }}</span>
                {% endfor %}
                {% for label in plugin.template_labels %}
                <span class="chip">{{ label }}</span>
                {% endfor %}
                <span class="chip">{{ plugin.hook_count }} hook(s)</span>
                <span class="chip">{{ plugin.config_count }} configs</span>
              </div>
              {% if plugin.required_plugins or plugin.required_binaries or plugin.output_mimetypes %}
              <div class="plugin-summary-facts">
                {% if False and plugin.required_plugins %}
                <div>{{ plugin.required_plugins|join(", ") }}</div>
                {% endif %}
                {% if plugin.required_binaries %}
                <div>{% for item in plugin.required_binaries[:2] %}<span class="chip chip--binary-summary">{{ item.display_name }}{% if item.min_version %}&gt;={{ item.min_version }}{% endif %} <small>({{ item.binproviders }})</small></span> {% endfor %}{% if plugin.required_binaries|length > 2 %}+{{ plugin.required_binaries|length - 2 }} more{% endif %}</div>
                {% endif %}
                {% if plugin.output_mimetypes %}
                <div>{% for item in plugin.output_mimetypes[:4] %}<span class="chip chip--mime chip--mime-{{ item.css_class }}">{{ item.emoji }} {{ item.label }}</span> {% endfor %}{% if plugin.output_mimetypes|length > 4 %}+{{ plugin.output_mimetypes|length - 4 }} more{% endif %}</div>
                {% endif %}
              </div>
              {% endif %}
            </div>
            <div class="plugin-corner-icon" aria-hidden="true">
              <div class="plugin-icon">{{ plugin.icon_html }}</div>
            </div>
          </summary>

          <div class="plugin-body">
            {% if plugin.description %}
            <p class="plugin-modal-description">{{ plugin.description }}</p>
            {% endif %}

            <div class="actions">
              <a class="button-link" href="{{ plugin.source_url }}" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Source on GitHub</a>
            </div>

            {% if plugin.required_plugins or plugin.required_binaries or plugin.output_mimetypes %}
            <h3 class="section-title">Dependencies &amp; Outputs</h3>
            <div class="plugin-info-grid">
              {% if plugin.required_plugins %}
              <article class="plugin-info-card">
                <span>Required Plugins</span>
                <div class="pill-list">
                  {% for item in plugin.required_plugins %}
                  <a href="#{{ item }}" class="chip chip--link">{{ item }}</a>
                  {% endfor %}
                </div>
              </article>
              {% endif %}
              {% if plugin.required_binaries %}
              <article class="plugin-info-card">
                <span>Required Binaries</span>
                <div class="pill-list">
                  {% for item in plugin.required_binaries %}
                  <span class="chip chip--binary" title="{{ item.title }}">
                    <code>{{ item.display_name }}</code>
                    <small>providers={{ item.binproviders }}</small>
                    {% if item.min_version %}
                    <small>min_version={{ item.min_version }}</small>
                    {% endif %}
                  </span>
                  {% endfor %}
                </div>
              </article>
              {% endif %}
              {% if plugin.output_mimetypes %}
              <article class="plugin-info-card">
                <span>Output Mimetypes</span>
                <div class="pill-list">
                  {% for item in plugin.output_mimetypes %}
                  <span class="chip chip--mime chip--mime-{{ item.css_class }}">{{ item.emoji }} {{ item.label }}</span>
                  {% endfor %}
                </div>
              </article>
              {% endif %}
            </div>
            {% endif %}

            <h3 class="section-title">Run It</h3>
            <div class="run-tabs" data-run-tabs>
              <div class="run-tabs-bar">
                <button type="button" class="run-tab active" data-run-tab="abx-dl">Run with <code>abx-dl</code></button>
                <button type="button" class="run-tab" data-run-tab="archivebox">Run with <code>archivebox</code></button>
              </div>
              <pre class="run-tab-panel active" data-run-panel="abx-dl"><code data-highlight-shell>{{ plugin.commands.abx_dl }}</code></pre>
              <pre class="run-tab-panel" data-run-panel="archivebox"><code data-highlight-shell>{{ plugin.commands.archivebox }}</code></pre>
            </div>
            <p class="note">{{ plugin.commands.note }}</p>

            <h3 class="section-title">Hook Scripts</h3>
            {% if plugin.hooks %}
            <div class="hook-list">
              {% for hook in plugin.hooks %}
              <article class="hook-card">
                <span class="hook-card-file"><a href="{{ hook.source_url }}" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">{{ hook.filename }}</a></span>
                <div class="hook-card-chips">
                  {% if hook.language_code == "py" %}
                  <span class="chip chip--lang chip--lang-py" title="Python">
                    <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" fill="none">
                      <path d="M12 3c-4.4 0-4.1 1.9-4.1 1.9v2h4.2v.6H6.2S3 7.1 3 12c0 4.9 2.8 4.7 2.8 4.7h1.7v-2.4s-.1-2.8 2.7-2.8h4.6s2.6 0 2.6-2.6V4.6S17.8 3 12 3Z" fill="currentColor" opacity="0.92"></path>
                      <path d="M12 21c4.4 0 4.1-1.9 4.1-1.9v-2h-4.2v-.6h5.9S21 16.9 21 12c0-4.9-2.8-4.7-2.8-4.7h-1.7v2.4s.1 2.8-2.7 2.8h-4.6S6.6 12.5 6.6 15v4.4S6.2 21 12 21Z" fill="currentColor" opacity="0.6"></path>
                      <circle cx="9.3" cy="5.6" r="1" fill="#fff"></circle>
                      <circle cx="14.7" cy="18.4" r="1" fill="#fff"></circle>
                    </svg>
                  </span>
                  {% elif hook.language_code == "js" %}
                  <span class="chip chip--lang chip--lang-js" title="JavaScript">
                    <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false">
                      <rect x="4.5" y="4.5" width="15" height="15" rx="2.5" fill="currentColor" opacity="0.2"></rect>
                      <path d="M10.3 8.1v6.4c0 2-1 3.4-3.1 3.4-1.7 0-2.7-.9-3.2-2l1.7-1c.3.6.6 1.1 1.4 1.1.7 0 1.1-.3 1.1-1.5V8.1h2.1Zm7.1 1.7c-.4-.7-1-.9-1.7-.9-.7 0-1.4.3-1.4 1 0 .7.5 1 1.8 1.4 1.8.6 3 1.3 3 3.3 0 2.1-1.7 3.3-3.9 3.3-2 0-3.2-.8-4-2.1l1.7-1.2c.5.8 1.1 1.4 2.2 1.4.9 0 1.6-.4 1.6-1.1 0-.8-.6-1-2-1.5-1.7-.6-2.8-1.3-2.8-3.2 0-1.9 1.6-3.1 3.7-3.1 1.4 0 2.5.4 3.3 1.6l-1.5 1.1Z" fill="currentColor"></path>
                    </svg>
                  </span>
                  {% endif %}
                  {% if hook.order is not none %}
                  <span class="chip">order {{ "%02d"|format(hook.order) }}</span>
                  {% endif %}
                  {% if hook.is_background %}
                  <span class="chip {{ 'chip--bg-daemon' if hook.is_daemon else 'chip--bg-finite' }}">background ({{ "daemon" if hook.is_daemon else "finite" }})</span>
                  {% else %}
                  <span class="chip chip--fg">foreground</span>
                  {% endif %}
                </div>
                <span class="hook-card-phase">{{ hook.phase }}</span>
              </article>
              {% endfor %}
            </div>
            {% else %}
            <div class="empty-state">No hook scripts are defined in this plugin directory.</div>
            {% endif %}

            <h3 class="section-title">Env Var Config Options</h3>
            {% if plugin.has_config %}
            <div class="config-table-wrap">
              <table class="config-table">
                <colgroup>
                  <col class="col-key">
                  <col class="col-default">
                  <col class="col-type">
                  <col class="col-aliases">
                </colgroup>
                <thead>
                  <tr>
                    <th>Key</th>
                    <th>Default</th>
                    <th>Type</th>
                    <th>Aliases / Fallback</th>
                  </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                  {% for field in plugin.config_fields %}
                  <tr>
                    <td><code>{{ field.key }}</code>{% if field.description %}<span class="config-key-desc">{{ field.description }}</span>{% endif %}</td>
                    <td class="cfg-default">{% if field.default is not none %}{{ field.default }}{% else %}<span class="config-table-muted">—</span>{% endif %}</td>
                    <td>
                      <code>{{ field.type }}</code>
                      {% if field.minimum is not none %}<br><small>min {{ field.minimum }}</small>{% endif %}
                      {% if field.pattern %}<br><small>pattern <code>{{ field.pattern }}</code></small>{% endif %}
                      {% if field.enum %}<br><small>{{ field.enum|join(" | ") }}</small>{% endif %}
                    </td>
                    <td>
                      {% if field.aliases %}<small>{{ field.aliases|join(", ") }}</small>{% endif %}
                      {% if field.fallback %}{% if field.aliases %}<br>{% endif %}<small>fallback: <code>{{ field.fallback }}</code></small>{% endif %}
                      {% if not field.aliases and not field.fallback %}<span class="config-table-muted">—</span>{% endif %}
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                  {% endfor %}
                </tbody>
              </table>
            </div>
            {% else %}
            <div class="empty-state">This plugin does not define a <code>config.json</code> schema.</div>
            {% endif %}
          </div>
        </details>
        {% endfor %}
      </main>

      <div class="empty-state" id="empty-state" hidden>No plugins match the current filter.</div>

      <footer class="page-footer">
        <div class="footer-intro">
          <h2>ArchiveBox ecosystem, plugins, and web archiving context</h2>
          <p>
            The web rots fast. News stories get edited, videos disappear, social posts vanish, and cited links break within a few years. ArchiveBox is an open-source self-hosted web archiving platform built to help individuals and organizations keep durable local copies of the web in standard formats like HTML, JSON, TXT, PDF, PNG, SQLite, and WARC.
          </p>
          <p>
            This marketplace documents the shared <a href="https://github.com/ArchiveBox/abx-plugins" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">abx-plugins</a> catalog used by <a href="https://github.com/ArchiveBox/ArchiveBox" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">ArchiveBox</a> and <a href="https://github.com/ArchiveBox/abx-dl" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">abx-dl</a>. ArchiveBox manages full collections and long-term archives, <a href="https://github.com/ArchiveBox/abx-dl" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">abx-dl</a> runs plugin pipelines directly, <a href="https://github.com/ArchiveBox/abx-pkg" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">abx-pkg</a> installs supporting binaries, and <a href="https://github.com/ArchiveBox/abx-plugins" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">abx-plugins</a> defines the hook scripts and config schemas that actually crawl pages, install tools, and extract per-site outputs.
          </p>
